{"id":20,"date":"2023-05-18T10:29:05","date_gmt":"2023-05-18T10:29:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/?page_id=20"},"modified":"2023-10-12T16:01:35","modified_gmt":"2023-10-12T16:01:35","slug":"faq","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/faq\/","title":{"rendered":"Popular Questions"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section alignfull alignfull\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__wrapper getwid-padding-tablet-top-large getwid-padding-tablet-bottom-large\" style=\"padding-top:175px;padding-bottom:140px\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__inner-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background-holder\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background has-background has-color-4-background-color\"><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__foreground\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__content\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__inner-content\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-style-wide-space is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion\" data-active-element=\"none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">How can I rent a bike or scooter from your website?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Renting a bike or scooter from our website is easy! Simply visit our homepage and click on the &#8220;Rent Now&#8221; button. You&#8217;ll be guided through a quick and seamless booking process to choose your desired bike or scooter, select the rental duration, and provide necessary details.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">What are the requirements for renting a bike or scooter?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>To rent a bike or scooter from our website, you must be at least 18 years old and possess a valid driver&#8217;s license. Additionally, we may require a refundable security deposit, which will be returned to you upon the safe and timely return of the rental vehicle.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">How long can I rent a bike or scooter for?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>You can rent a bike or scooter for a minimum of 1 hour up to a maximum of 24 hours. If you need a longer rental period, please contact our customer support team, and we&#8217;ll be happy to assist you.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion\" data-active-element=\"none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">Do you provide helmets and safety gear?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Yes, safety is our top priority. We provide helmets and basic safety gear with every bike or scooter rental. It is essential to wear a helmet while riding, and we strongly encourage you to follow all local traffic laws and regulations for your safety.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">Can I cancel or modify my reservation?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Yes, we understand that plans can change. You can cancel or modify your reservation up to 24 hours before the scheduled rental start time. Please note that a cancellation fee may apply, depending on the timing and terms of cancellation.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">What happens if the bike or scooter gets damaged during my rental period?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>In case of any damage to the rental vehicle during your rental period, please inform our customer support team immediately. The extent of liability for damage will be assessed on a case-by-case basis. It&#8217;s important to review our rental agreement and terms of service to understand the specific guidelines related to damage and liability.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":108,"featured_media":147,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"template-canvas-header-page.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/20"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/108"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=20"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/20\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4415,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/20\/revisions\/4415"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/147"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-bike\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=20"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}